data.description: GORGEOUS move-in ready home with updates galore! Designer fixtures, vinyl plank flooring, farmhouse kitchen, & remodeled bathroom! Tons of natural light & high ceilings bring another level of open concept to this stunning home. Spacious island kitchen features abundance of cabinets, breakfast bar & oversized dining area. Cozy up to the fireplace in 2-story family room & don't miss the extra nook under the staircase! Downstairs primary bedroom features en-suite bathroom with separate shower, garden tub, 2 sinks & 2 large walk-in closets! Upstairs is a huge game-room, bonus loft area, 3 bedrooms & 2 bathrooms. Big backyard is ready for private pool as it backs up to Estates section so rear neighbor is far into distance. Live in beautiful GATED community of Legends Ranch with events, lakes, walking trails, pools, parks & splash pad. Zoned to highly rated Conroe ISD & Grand Oaks H.S. Just minutes away from The Woodlands amenities! Easy access I-45, 99 & Hardy Toll! No flooding! MUST SEE!
